    <refsect2><title><anchor role="function" id="Geoclue.AddReference"/>AddReference ()</title><indexterm><primary>AddReference</primary><secondary>Geoclue</secondary></indexterm><programlisting>AddReference ()</programlisting>Increase the reference count on the provider. 
				Provider may shutdown if reference count reaches zero, so 
				using AddReference()/RemoveReference is important for clients needing server
				persistence -- basically any client that uses SetOptions() or connects to
				signals.<variablelist role="params"/></refsect2>
